      "title": "Thirteen people arrested over unruly behaviour at filling stations",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The police have arrested 13 people who were engaged in unruly behaviour at filling stations in separate incidents reported from 11 areas since yesterday.",
        "Two of them were taken into custody early this morning for behaving in an unruly manner near a filling station in Polonnaruwa police area, while under the influence of alcohol.",
        "In another development, a man from Angunukolapelessa who was obstructing the duties of police officers at a filling station in Hungama area was placed under arrest."
      ],
